OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRapid cancer diagnosis     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcentre rollout a UK first  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Wales has become the first part of the 
OL,6, UK to roll-out centres that can help   
OL,7, diagnose people with cancer in days.   
OL,9,FNational cancer clinical director Prof 
OL,10,FTom Crosby said rapid diagnostic       
OL,11,Fcentres (RDCs) were a "huge step" in   
OL,12,Faddressing Wales' long waiting times.  
OL,14,FBut he warned cancer services faced    
OL,15,Ftheir biggest challenge while a charity
OL,16,Fwarned of a "perilous" situation.      
OL,18,FPatients and cancer charities welcomed 
OL,19,Fthe centres, but insisted more needed  
OL,20,Fto be done.                            
